When one guy noshing from a bowl of something - or - other at an outdoor cafe was asked if he was proud to be an American , he replied " no . " When pushed further for a reason , he offered two words : " Donald Trump . " He added that " the sooner they can get rid of Donald Trump , the better the future is gon na be . " Said diner also was asked if patriotism is a good thing . As before he answered " no . " And his reason ? " It creates division , " he said . " It 's like religion .
